      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:4:54:8",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ( صلى الله عليه وآله ) فِي جَنِينِ الْبَهِيمَةِ إِذَا ضُرِبَتْ فَأَزْلَقَتْ عُشْرُ ثَمَنِهَا ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Al Nowfaly, from Al Sakuny, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> said regarding a foetus of the animal when it is truck, so it aborts it, (the compensation is) being one-tenth of its price’."
        ]
